726060f-a.text:
Astoria Boulevard, north side, adjoining (to the west) the intersection of Main Avenue, showing an old house, 80 yards back of Astoria Boulevard. 28th Avenue passes directly in front of the house, running parallel to the Boulevard, and was formerly
known as Tisdale Street.
P. L. Sperr  March 6, 1931
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
